headline: CAH Strengthens Distribution With New Consumer Health Logistics Hub
summary: Cardinal Health opens a 350,000-square-foot Consumer Health Logistics Center in Ohio, strengthening its pharmaceutical supply chain and advancing its multiyear infrastructure expansion strategy.
